name: Sloppasaur.GitHub.io
tagline: Just a testing website... Might become something better soon
body:
## Welcome to my page!
Hello everyone! I'm still kind of new to coding, so please bear with me while I strive to get better and further develop my programming skills. While my projects are minor, I'll keep posting on my progress.

## A little about myself
* I'm still learning a bit of coding, but I've developed a little skill in:
  * Java - The first language I started learning, I was pretty decent until I stopped and forgot how to use it.
  * Python - The 
  * HTML
  * All of which I'm still currently learning
* I play a few instruments, those being the violin for 6 years, and the piano for 2. Until I discovered programming I always thought I would major in the music industry.
* I'm definitely an _**AVID**_ Cross Fitter. I will always set aside time to a workout and improve my fitness level.

## A Big Note
This Website is still being developed,as I've just finished trying out [using GitHub Flavored Markdown](https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/) so changes should still be occurring periodically or when I manage to have the time.

### Goals

- [x] Make a GitHub account
- [x] Start developing a Website of sorts
- [ ] Become proficient at HTML
- [ ] Become proficient at Python
- [ ] Become proficient at Java
- [ ] Become proficient at C++
- [ ] Become proficient at CSS
- [ ] Finish a website
- [ ] Make it to Regionals at Cross Fit
- [ ] Completed the list
